  "body": "### Description\nConsensus layer will communicate via engineForkChoiceUpdated the current head and latest finalized blocks.  Presently the latest finalized block is only held in memory and will be absent on restart.  Besu needs to persist the latest finalized block when it receives it, and load this value on restart.\n\n\n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n* persist latest finalized block to underlying storage\n* load finalized block from underlying storage on restart\n\n",
